data.description: This wonderful home is located on a quiet street in the  Indian Wells community. You are sure to love the split floor plan, vaulted ceilings, formal dining room plus a breakfast nook just off the kitchen. Located in the heart of the home, the kitchen offers wood cabinets, granite counter tops, mosaic glass backsplash, stainless steel appliances and bar seating. Both the interior and exterior were painted recently and the roof and AC are 10 years old. Enjoy peace and serenity from your covered and screened pool area overlooking 2 water features and a synthetic grass backyard. You are centrally located near great shopping and dining. Information herein deemed reliable and subject to errors, omissions, or changes without notice. All measurements are approximate.
